originalText.text: I called this office last week to ask if the Dr is in fact a Pain Management Dr and if he took a specific insurance and the receptionist Leilani couldn't answer anything,  she must have asked someone and came back and said yes. I called back today to schedule the apptand before I could even talk she hung up on me.  I called back and she now said that the Dr is not available and they only do physical therapy.  This office is super unprofessional and you should not even waste your time with then.
